<item>
            <title>[FLINK-26783] Restore from a stop-with-savepoint if failed during committing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-26783</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We decided stop-with-savepoint should commit side-effects and thus we should fail over to those savepoints if a failure happens when committing side effects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13434915">FLINK-26783</key>
            <summary>Restore from a stop-with-savepoint if failed during committing</summary>
